# Implementation Plan - Comic Mode Scaffolding

## Goal Description
Scaffold the directory structure for the new "Comic Mode" and implement the initial files to support the "Dual-Mode Strategy" (Cinematic + Comic) as defined in the project documentation.

## User Review Required
> [!NOTE]
> I will be creating a new top-level `modes` directory in `src` to house `comic` and `cinematic` (existing) logic, or just `comic` if cinematic is the default. Based on standard patterns, I'll place it in `src/modes/comic`.

## Proposed Changes

### Directory Structure
#### [NEW] `src/modes/comic/engine`
- Dedicated folder for Canvas logic and interaction handling.

#### [NEW] `src/stores`
- `comicStore.ts`: State management for Pages, Panels, and Bubbles.

#### [EXISTING] `src/modes/comic/layouts`
- `ComicLayout.tsx`: Updated to strictly enforce "Dark Jewel-Tone" glassmorphism (UI is dark, canvas paper is light).

### File Implementation

#### [NEW] [ComicCanvas.tsx](file:///Users/apoaaron/.gemini/antigravity/Nano%20Banana%20Expanded/src/modes/comic/engine/ComicCanvas.tsx)
- Wrapper for the infinite drag-and-drop stage.

#### [NEW] [InteractionLayer.tsx](file:///Users/apoaaron/.gemini/antigravity/Nano%20Banana%20Expanded/src/modes/comic/engine/InteractionLayer.tsx)
- Handles selection, resizing, and layering of elements.

#### [NEW] [comicStore.ts](file:///Users/apoaaron/.gemini/antigravity/Nano%20Banana%20Expanded/src/stores/comicStore.ts)
- Zustand store for Comic Mode state.

#### [MODIFY] [ComicLayout.tsx](file:///Users/apoaaron/.gemini/antigravity/Nano%20Banana%20Expanded/src/modes/comic/layouts/ComicLayout.tsx)
- Ensure background is `bg-neutral-900` or darker.
- UI elements must use glassmorphic jewel-tones.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- None for this initial scaffolding.

### Manual Verification
- Verify directories are created.
- Verify files exist.
- (Future) Import `ComicLayout` into `App.tsx` or a route to verify it renders.
